      <title>印度警方在恰蒂斯加尔邦打死 29 名疑似毛派叛乱分子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/indian-police-kill-29-suspected-maoist-rebels-in-chhattisgarh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，距离全国投票开始三天，印度中部恰蒂斯加尔邦发生枪战，至少 29 名疑似毛派叛乱分子被打死，一名安全人员受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/indian-police-kill-29-suspected-maoist-rebels-in-chhattisgarh</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 15:29:26 GMT</pubDate>
